2017-02-01T07:53:55Z", "closed_at": "2017-02-01T07:53:51Z", "author_association": "OWNER", "body_html": "<p>When I try to save an application draft, I get this error:<br>\n\"Validation failed: Country can't be blank\"</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1745735/22226888/aa051292-e1c8-11e6-8d14-c1acc1f83c4d.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1745735/22226888/aa051292-e1c8-11e6-8d14-c1acc1f83c4d.png\" alt=\"save-app-draft\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>This happened because the Location field in my User Profile was not filled out (it was not required before <a href=\"https://github.com/rails-girls-summer-of-code/rgsoc-teams/issues/593\" class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"199366330\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/rails-girls-summer-of-code/rgsoc-teams/issues/593\">#593</a>).</p>\n<p>We should show a normal error message on the application draft edit form in case some fields in associated User Profiles are missing.</p>", "body_text": "When I try to save an application draft, I get this error:\n\"Validation failed: Country can't be blank\"\n\nThis happened because the Location field in my User Profile was not filled out (it was not required before #593).\nWe should show a normal error message on the application draft edit form in case some fields in associated User Profiles are missing.", "body": "When I try to save an application draft, I get this error: \r\n\"Validation failed: Country can't be blank\"\r\n\r\n![save-app-draft](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1745735/22226888/aa051292-e1c8-11e6-8d14-c1acc1f83c4d.png)\r\n\r\nThis happened because the Location field in my User Profile was not filled out (it was not required before https://github.com/rails-girls-summer-of-code/rgsoc-teams/issues/593). \r\n\r\nWe should show a normal error message on the application draft edit form in case some fields in associated User Profiles are missing. \r\n\r\n\r\n"}